{
  "stem": "27507.5",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The grown-ups, some of the-- I must say that I'm not 100% aware to what extent they worked.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think I was [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] not so aware of that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But they must have worked, because the-- the uncle who was a doctor, he certainly worked.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the uncles who were having the-- who were working in the workshop, they worked.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were there during the day, so they were working.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And-- but never went-- I was never in the place where they worked, so I was not aware of all that.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the one that I remember that did work was-- if I remember seeing working who was a cousin, an older cousin, one of-- Bolek, who was a cousin of my mother.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he was for a while conductor of one of those horse-coaches.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And when I was going to school in [POLISH] Street, in there, in probably it was already in early '42, that was-- I was going near to place where those-- the end station of that-- of that coach service.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he would-- and he was sometimes there, and-- because he was a conductor.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he would let me make-- go on the coach when it was making a loop round from the-- when it was turning round.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And that was something that I was very keen on.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Otherwise, I had-- then we moved in early '42, late '41 or early '42, something like that, my father did manage to find another flat in [POLISH], in the same street that I described before, but in another part of the street, which still was part of the ghetto in [POLISH].",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was another big house.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Somehow that was a nicer house than where we lived before.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the flat was nicer.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
